text: The 2011 Primera B season was the 61st completed season of the Primera B de Chile. ==Torneo Apertura== Deportes Antofagasta was tournament’s champion. ==Torneo Clausura== Everton de Viña del Mar was tournament’s champion. ==References== ==External links== * RSSSF 2011 Category:Primera B de Chile seasons Primera B
title: 2011 Primera B de Chile season
